lead_paragraph: Tomas Berdych battled the elements and a gritty display by unseeded Croatian Ivan Dodig at a rain-ravaged Wimbledon on Wednesday, sealing a four-set victory he admitted should have been his the previous day.

headline.print_headline: Coachless Berdych Battles to Four-Set Win at Rain-Hit Wimbledon
headline.main: Coachless Berdych Battles to Four-Set Win at Rain-Hit Wimbledon
